Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.11,0:01:02.46,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以說 關於這題…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.46,0:01:04.21,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,蛤? 聽不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.48,0:01:09.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,赤木… 你為什麼要和我交往啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.19,0:01:10.19,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,小亮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.83,0:01:12.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不該叫赤木而是小正吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.20,0:01:15.99,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你真要叫這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.36,0:01:19.11,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不老實這麼叫 我就不幫你做題了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.52,0:01:22.74,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,小正…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.78,0:01:25.57,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,聽不到呢 你再近點說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.17,0:01:27.09,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,小正!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.53,0:01:30.91,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真是!! 現在在討論很正經的問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.12,0:01:32.69,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,明明親一下就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.79,0:01:35.68,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我是在問你和我交往是喜歡我哪裡!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.94,0:01:38.20,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,唔… 哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.38,0:01:43.82,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以說現在在討論很正經的問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.88,0:01:45.49,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,明明親一下就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.72,0:01:48.01,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,小亮的優點?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.32,0:01:49.19,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,臉吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.26,0:01:51.93,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,蛤!? 那性格什麼的都無所謂了?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.26,0:01:54.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是小亮你長得很可愛唷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.30,0:01:57.17,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你都完全沒關注我的內在嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.21,0:01:58.89,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,因為 小亮很可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.06,0:02:01.07,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不對 所以說不是這個問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.22,0:02:02.68,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,很可愛唷 小亮～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.82,0:02:04.66,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊!真是的! 好囉嗦啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.50,0:02:08.62,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那 要是有比我可愛的女生不馬上就變心了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.82,0:02:09.95,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嘛 可能性也…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.97,0:02:10.61,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,去死!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.91,0:02:13.55,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,別鬧彆扭嘛 還有好多其他優點唷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.03,0:02:14.86,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,比如胸…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.98,0:02:17.08,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,長相也好胸部也好全是這些
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.17,0:02:19.31,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你根本就沒關注過我的內在對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.51,0:02:21.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真是的… 我沒說過這種話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.36,0:02:25.30,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我可是一直 有想要關注小亮的內在美的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:27.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那 我哪裡好?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.24,0:02:28.85,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.27,0:02:32.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒有… 一個都?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.93,0:02:33.64,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.82,0:02:36.36,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,正如你自己說的那樣 又易怒又粗野
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.94,0:02:38.90,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真對不起了呢… 反正我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.92,0:02:41.77,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這種喜歡鬧彆扭的性子也很麻煩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.12,0:02:44.97,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真是的! 那趕緊分手不就好了嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.02,0:02:46.87,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你又說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.50,0:02:49.54,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,雖然你到處都是缺點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.61,0:02:51.82,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,囉嗦! 我什麼都不想聽!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.63,0:02:53.63,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是喜歡你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.61,0:02:58.03,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,反正你也會說喜歡胸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:03:00.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,也喜歡小亮你的性格喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.78,0:03:03.35,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,易怒的性子也好粗野的性子也好全部包含在內
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.35,0:03:04.75,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我對小亮你…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.13,0:03:06.11,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,無比LOVE
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.96,0:03:09.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,開心的話表現出來也沒關係喲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.52,0:03:10.87,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,好煩啊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.95,0:03:12.19,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是是真的唷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.34,0:03:14.55,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,雖說因為你太可愛總忍不住想欺負
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:18.20,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那 再說一遍 喜歡我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.79,0:03:21.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯? 不用說「最喜歡」也沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.27,0:03:22.97,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那就說「最喜歡」!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.14,0:03:25.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,「請說」 才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.32,0:03:27.38,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,請說…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.61,0:03:28.36,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,「小正」呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.49,0:03:30.48,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,喂 你快說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:31.64,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,小亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.51,0:03:33.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.67,0:03:38.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,前不久和男友氛圍很好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.51,0:03:40.94,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是沒能成功
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.66,0:03:45.28,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,最近連電視劇也都是特攝了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:46.60,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那之後總感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.71,0:03:49.01,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,說相互之間都不太積極也好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.19,0:03:51.40,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,說在逃避著這種事也好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.93,0:03:52.66,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.77,0:03:57.58,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是覺得前不久那件事沒成功很丟臉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.26,0:04:00.39,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是我對這件事完全不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.62,0:04:02.58,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,再加把勁對我出手也沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.96,0:04:05.91,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,說來 要是我來說這話總覺得有點那個呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.00,0:04:07.34,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以香奈你看過嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.53,0:04:10.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦!?那個 在聊什麼來的?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:10.71,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,砰～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.74,0:04:11.30,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.62,0:04:12.92,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,在聊電視劇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.92,0:04:14.60,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,最近「砰」也總是老樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:16.49,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不是說好在電視劇裡找新梗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.53,0:04:20.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,總而言之 先設定為警察和犯人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.79,0:04:22.90,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,等等 那個我沒看過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.04,0:04:25.18,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒事的 我會起勁的演的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:26.35,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,香奈也起勁的跟著來～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.72,0:04:29.98,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,說實話 現在梗什麼的都無所謂呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:33.82,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,FBI!! 兩手放到腦後!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:35.25,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,等 等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.28,0:04:37.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,眼睛閉上 不要反抗!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.64,0:04:41.58,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,蠢貨 大意了吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:47.20,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,呼呼… 您也是惡人呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:49.29,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,代…代官您才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:49.29,comment,,0,0,0,,註：日本時代劇裡面這兩句話作為惡衙役與壞商人之間的標準對白而廣為傳播。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:49.29,comment,,0,0,0,,日語對白：「お主も悪よのう」「お代官こそ…」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.45,0:04:52.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那個 中途好像換角色了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,0:04:55.37,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 也是呢 哈哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.04,0:04:59.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,難道說這傢伙 準備親我的?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.63,0:05:01.28,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,（害羞…）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.62,0:05:04.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦?咦? 難道這是段子裡的劇情?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:07.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不不不… 不會吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:09.55,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那這回 我演外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.59,0:05:11.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不會吧!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.71,0:05:13.60,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這次 香奈你來當FBI
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.07,0:05:15.94,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那個 我盡力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:17.80,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,就假設下喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:19.37,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,就算他剛才是準備親我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.43,0:05:20.83,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這劇本應該沒辦法再…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.04,0:05:25.66,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不會吧! 不會吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:28.81,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不要靠近了! 再靠近就射你喔!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.04,0:05:30.26,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,砰～砰～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.33,0:05:33.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,認真的!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:44.75,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,就這感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.71,0:05:46.83,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 就那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:48.67,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這梗結尾不好笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.76,0:05:50.71,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不再仔細構思一下的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.92,0:05:52.08,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那個啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.72,0:05:57.69,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,回去吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:05:58.54,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.99,0:06:02.86,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我聽說你喜歡電影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.23,0:06:04.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你有時間的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.06,0:06:07.20,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,也不是不可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.66,0:06:09.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那明天電影院見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.25,0:06:15.79,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,山根閣下 考試怎麼樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.82,0:06:17.46,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,本山君 還行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.82,0:06:20.09,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,剛剛是在想明天的安排嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.18,0:06:22.91,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不記得了! 你說什麼呢聽不懂…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.95,0:06:25.21,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,明天不是說好和我一起去看電影嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:29.09,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,其實我太期待了以至於沒心思考試呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:31.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,約好的是明天的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.79,0:06:35.19,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,喔呀 忘了嗎?不是要看魔法小新嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.19,0:06:38.69,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我可是每年都看不夠魔法小新的啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.28,0:06:41.74,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這個啊 明天以後不可以嗎 其實我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:48.29,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,莫非 不是有女孩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:48.59,comment,,0,0,0,,怨(女)念(人)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:51.03,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:55.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哈哈哈 跟你開玩笑呢 山根閣下怎麼會有女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.08,0:06:56.43,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,當然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:06:59.32,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那些嘲笑我們挫男的傲慢的豬們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.32,0:07:02.24,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不值得我們浪費寶貴的青春
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.24,0:07:04.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,必 必須的 我也討厭女孩的唷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:06.89,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這次也是被男性朋友約…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.04,0:07:09.45,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,喔呀 你除了我還有別的朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.34,0:07:12.81,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,中 中學時候的朋友啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.92,0:07:14.21,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,偶爾也會一起見個面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.21,0:07:15.98,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:20.28,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那我本山友道就把這個預約讓出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.92,0:07:22.94,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我們總是遭人鄙棄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.28,0:07:25.70,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,因此朋友之間的羈絆是至高無上的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:27.93,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,下次給我介紹介紹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.03,0:07:30.22,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,本 本山君!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.57,0:07:32.78,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}電影我一個人看就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.19,0:07:33.57,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,多好的人啊 本山君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.77,0:07:35.23,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,然而我卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:39.25,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我卻不惜說謊去跟女生…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:41.26,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那明天電影院見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.84,0:07:44.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我這樣的人渣不需要女孩!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:47.31,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉本山君 我說謊了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.33,0:07:48.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:49.35,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,朋友什麼的不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.47,0:07:51.82,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,通訊錄也就只有你和家裡的電話 其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.82,0:07:52.95,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,山根閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.23,0:07:55.85,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你居然能告訴我這麼羞恥的事實
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.90,0:07:58.97,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我還是第一次有你這樣的推心置腹的朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.14,0:08:01.67,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,本山君!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.00,0:08:04.58,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,明天山根閣下有其他事情的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.73,0:08:06.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,既然是特地隱瞞的事情的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.85,0:08:08.65,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我也不會深究的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:11.03,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒關係的 既然是朋友就全部告訴你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.24,0:08:14.94,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,其實是被一個不熟的女生邀請去看電影了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.40,0:08:19.12,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,其實之前也有一起吃過飯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.26,0:08:21.37,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是那時候完全聊不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.41,0:08:22.45,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不知道為什麼被邀請了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.55,0:08:33.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不惜跟我說謊也要隱瞞的事情竟然是女孩!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.91,0:08:36.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉本山君 但是明天會和你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.52,0:08:38.94,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這種時候當然該選女朋友啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.96,0:08:44.29,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,當然我也很討厭女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.38,0:08:48.51,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,她們看髒東西一樣的那雙眼睛我恨不得全弄瞎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.86,0:08:53.97,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是話雖如此 願意和山根閣下一樣的挫男說話的純潔的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:56.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我怎麼能有意見呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.33,0:08:58.67,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我… 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:01.23,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真替你高興啊啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.30,0:09:04.46,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,本山啊啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.71,0:09:08.23,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你跟那個女生已經在交往了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.26,0:09:10.26,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能 並沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:11.65,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真的只是普通朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.68,0:09:13.27,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是說朋友其實也有點冒昧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.31,0:09:16.59,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,她怎麼想的我也不清楚怎麼個狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.67,0:09:18.64,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,原來如此 單純的交際嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.00,0:09:21.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,可以的話本山君也一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.36,0:09:23.21,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,她也可能帶朋友過去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.26,0:09:24.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,要是你不反感的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:06:00.13,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\pos(174.4,586.8)\fs40\c&H001E1E1E\b1\bord0}結\N束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:28.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,山根閣下的朋友的話沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:29.17,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\pos(174.4,586.8)\fs40\c&H001E1E1E\b1\bord0}結\N束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.45,0:09:33.65,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,經常有人來找我諮詢戀愛方面的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.06,0:09:36.45,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是我還沒有跟人交往過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.42,0:09:40.52,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,為什麼要找我商量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.69,0:09:41.95,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我也想談場…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:43.28,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.77,0:09:46.41,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,誰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.53,0:09:50.21,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 但是我並沒有俯視女生的愛好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.13,0:09:53.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,搞什麼這個男的 為什麼在樹上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.14,0:09:55.65,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,出來吧小貓咪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:03.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你剛是救了一下不來的小貓咪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.47,0:10:05.92,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,什麼 只是想爬一下樹而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:07.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以 你在煩惱什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.76,0:10:09.24,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,果然聽到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.48,0:10:13.83,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,並不 只是你跟那隻貓一樣露著困擾著的眼神啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:16.52,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,喵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.89,0:10:21.92,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這個人怎麼回事 把人比作可愛的小貓咪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:25.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,莫非你覺得我是戀愛達人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.07,0:10:27.30,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,欸 也不至於
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.73,0:10:28.77,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,正解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.53,0:10:32.43,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,戀愛達人?你覺得很帥氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.72,0:10:34.60,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎麼會帥氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.51,0:10:40.11,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這種人更多地是弄哭女生而不是讓女生笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:43.86,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,糟糕 我要是有達人的名頭的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.92,0:10:46.22,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,會惹怒戀愛的神明的 糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:49.23,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,好帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.16,0:10:51.40,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這感覺怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.84,0:10:53.89,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我 對這個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.20,0:10:57.08,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,來吧 什麼都可以跟我說的 可以的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.67,0:11:00.51,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你 是我的王子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.94,0:11:01.55,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:03.40,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那跟我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.44,0:11:04.80,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這可不行喲 小貓咪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.08,0:11:06.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,因為我是大家的王子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.26,0:11:09.60,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,看上我的話 會受傷的唷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.53,0:11:12.91,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這樣也沒關係!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.16,0:11:16.63,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那是殘像喲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.99,0:11:21.20,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,放棄吧小貓咪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.41,0:11:23.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,誰也沒辦法抓住我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:26.60,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:30.45,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,來吧 像剛剛救那隻貓一樣救我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.70,0:11:31.74,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,喵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.93,0:11:33.43,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,救救我 喵～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.95,0:11:35.28,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,讓人困擾的小貓咪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.64,0:11:42.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,滑～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:50.51,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,血 血要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.64,0:11:53.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒事的 白天吃的義大利麵條而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:56.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,對不起 都怪我做愚蠢的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.56,0:11:59.03,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,愚蠢的事? 指什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.97,0:12:04.32,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,救助受困的小貓咪是王子的職責呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.26,0:12:06.91,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,喜歡!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:08.59,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,再見啦 小貓咪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.92,0:12:10.56,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不要再做危險的事情了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.23,0:12:14.03,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,最後 最後至少告訴我名字
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.82,0:12:17.30,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,香取慎一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:18.61,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.04,0:12:23.59,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,香取前輩!
Comment: 0,0:00:55.16,0:00:57.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,-------------------ED-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:50.48,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}閉じ込めたくて  だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:55.90,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}あなたに出会えたことで
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:12:02.45,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}強くいられたんだ ずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:07.62,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}明日も目が覚めたとき
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:13.50,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}すぐ隣にいる  と思ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:19.59,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}ただそれだけでいいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:50.48,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}鎖進我的心裡  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:55.90,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}想與你相見這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:12:02.45,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}卻很需要勇氣  一直如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:07.62,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}明明只是希望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:13.50,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}明天當我  睜開眼的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:19.59,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}你能在我身旁而已
Comment: 0,0:00:55.16,0:00:57.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,-------------------OP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.98,0:00:17.90,children opjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}些細な出来事さえも特別だって思うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.26,0:00:24.69,children opjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}ほらね今も君のこと考えちゃうの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.65,0:00:32.50,children opjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}好きと嫌い交互に数えてゆく占い
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.72,0:00:36.36,children opjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}2分の (1の) 確率 (それじゃ)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.42,0:00:40.44,children opjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}踏み出せないね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.27,0:00:48.74,children opjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}きっと あぁ この関係は曖昧模糊っていうのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.90,0:00:54.18,children opjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}徒然でも I wish I feel my sweet
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.37,0:00:58.29,children opjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}大事にしなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.98,0:00:17.90,children opch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}微不足道的事情也會覺得很特別
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.26,0:00:24.69,children opch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}此時此刻也在想念著你的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.65,0:00:32.50,children opch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}喜歡與討厭相互交替的占卜
